Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.76,0:00:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当月光照射黑夜之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.50,0:00:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说 促使宇宙舞动着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.20,0:00:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的决斗展开时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.31,0:00:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遥远的地方 呼喊着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.82,0:00:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(超重神)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.69,0:00:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪恶为此而戴上了面具\N希望能以此错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.43,0:00:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换取持续戮力不停\N所追求的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.77,0:00:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为命运而不知所措之\N叹息的玫瑰念珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.24,0:00:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因无法抹去的记忆\N而为爱颤抖着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.25,0:01:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当月光照亮黑夜之时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.06,0:01:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说促使得宇宙舞动着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.93,0:01:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虚幻的坠天使们啊\N美丽的飞翔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.03,0:01:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在禁忌的决斗展开时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.74,0:01:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死神正自遥远的地方呼喊着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.69,0:01:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.86,0:01:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,删除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.12,0:01:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将所有的人类...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.83,0:01:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的存在...删除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.56,0:01:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探测出他们的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.66,0:01:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.87,0:01:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因应该区域的条件...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.40,0:01:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用最佳的方法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.50,0:01:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,删除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.47,0:01:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遭遇障碍时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.64,0:01:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对应该条件...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.98,0:01:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使用最佳的方法...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.25,0:01:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,排除障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.75,0:02:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该命令效期...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.98,0:02:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无限制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.76,0:02:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.73,0:02:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么超重机组们的机体\N全都遍体鳞伤啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.26,0:02:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的进化比\N桑德曼先生预测的还要快吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.04,0:02:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.78,0:02:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果进化目的只是要屠杀人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.85,0:02:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不需要这种破坏力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.33,0:02:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种是为了\N对付超重神而展开进化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了、不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.93,0:02:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快想办法才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊这个就是这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.77,0:02:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第十三话 白银之牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦不过是\N总统亲临的公开发表会而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戒备还真是森严啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.75,0:03:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是四木重工的直升机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.19,0:03:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.59,0:03:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,军需品公司也相当感兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对外星异种用的机动组件啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.43,0:03:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎样的机械啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.50,0:04:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好我们的战斗机\N会变得可以变形、合体呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.94,0:04:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后变成像超重神\N那种巨型的机械人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.61,0:04:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想坐上去哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.19,0:04:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基本的作业\N请依照指导手册去进行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.66,0:04:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后媚月小姐跟莉露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在反电磁力场产生装置\N开始运转时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.86,0:04:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请检查电装系统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是、是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.03,0:04:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.04,0:04:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.34,0:04:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在上次的踢腿后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.47,0:04:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G攻击机的合神部分的轴组\N跟装甲的负荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.01,0:04:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远远的超过了\N耐久基准数值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.25,0:04:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要仔细
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.62,0:04:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并接受朵莉雅的指示来作检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.25,0:04:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的又不是我踢的\N是斗牙踢的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.15,0:04:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不都是因为你没考虑到后果\N乱踢一通的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.42,0:04:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.39,0:04:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琉菜小姐也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.43,0:05:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能够多考虑一下\N重钻机的回转方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟推送轴的运动能量的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不都是因为你没考虑到后果\N乱钻一通的关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.44,0:05:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.07,0:05:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两位请不要吵架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.91,0:05:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎样啦\N什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.98,0:05:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对、对不起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.31,0:05:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸的气息完全一致呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.05,0:05:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个真是相亲相爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.62,0:05:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会跟这种女人...\N谁会跟这种东西...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.72,0:05:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种情形下\N真的能修得完吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.13,0:05:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题我们也会加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.96,0:05:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱娜一起加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.67,0:05:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.18,0:05:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.19,0:06:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对准人类、地球的侵略者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.16,0:06:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.89,0:06:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一天比一天强大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.33,0:06:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们EFA
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.86,0:06:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了地球真正的和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.90,0:06:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的力量现在正式诞生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.47,0:06:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦这个不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来相当具有广用性呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.85,0:06:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实战的配备从什么时候开始呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的体型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.06,0:06:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉雅曾报告说外星异种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.60,0:06:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了彻底破坏超重神\N而展开了进化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.77,0:06:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.04,0:06:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许已经到了该把"那个"\N托付给我们的骑士之时了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.58,0:07:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定要看清楚才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.05,0:07:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确定他们是否真的有足以\N被托付予白银之牙的资格吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.46,0:07:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驰骋于天际
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.34,0:07:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞奔于海面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将主宰着宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.42,0:07:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便是我们EFA的荣耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对外星异种用之机动组件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.37,0:07:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真惊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.94,0:08:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦差不多要登场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾力克斯队长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.48,0:08:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从正上方\N有未确认部队急速接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.28,0:08:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是陨石?不在减速中\N该不会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.03,0:08:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其名为...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.27,0:08:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.79,0:08:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生紧急状况!发生紧急状况!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.93,0:08:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种出现在地球联合政府大楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.63,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在当地进行迎击的EFA空军部队\N以及地面部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已呈现毁灭状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.78,0:09:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总统亲临的公开发表会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成了空欢喜一场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.68,0:09:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在外星异种\N处于完全静默状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.79,0:09:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼这次的敌人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.26,0:09:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.23,0:09:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.20,0:09:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎外星异种比起屠杀人类\N反而更有兴趣与我们的骑士决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时机刚刚好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.87,0:09:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让彻夜修理有了意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.24,0:09:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯大家都很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.68,0:09:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媚月小姐您的脸色不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.85,0:09:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?没事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.15,0:09:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我最近老是睡不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.62,0:09:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也没问题吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.09,0:09:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全没睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.29,0:10:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.40,0:10:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼超重神都整修完毕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以迎击哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.04,0:10:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战骑的诸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无法许可各位迎击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.15,0:10:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为、为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没听到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.65,0:10:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准出击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.42,0:10:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.56,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为外星异种\N的目标是超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外星异种...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以超重神为目标?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人在第一次攻击后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.21,0:10:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有活动迹象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.44,0:10:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是在等待\N等着超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.51,0:10:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就更不应该避之不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.51,0:10:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对方既然下了战帖...\N 笨蛋好好想一想..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.32,0:11:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕对方已经进化到可以应付\N超重神所有的攻击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.02,0:11:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该已经进化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的超重神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.49,0:11:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有足以造成\N那个外星异种损伤的武器吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.17,0:11:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不怕超重神武器的外星异种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.97,0:11:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就不让我们去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.24,0:11:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的战斗应该不是\N只为了我们自己的存亡而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.12,0:11:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够守护重要的人们或事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.56,0:11:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那才是我们地球战骑队...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才是超重神所应进行的战斗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.83,0:11:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这时候畏惧不敢迎战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.10,0:11:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就没有脸去见绫香了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.00,0:11:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.84,0:11:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行以超重神目前的装备...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.08,0:12:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位武器的话这里有哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.55,0:12:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开发编号:XB-04
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试作型剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重万断剑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.13,0:12:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然反应上有些许难处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.03,0:12:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但破坏力可称得上削铁如泥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.13,0:12:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刀身上的耐重力子结晶涂装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.07,0:12:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也在武装班的成员\N努力下完美地完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.77,0:12:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大致上所有的敌人\N都可以一刀两断的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帅啊! 太帅了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.71,0:12:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就没话说了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.71,0:12:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要出发啰!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.72,0:12:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.85,0:12:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然外观有点粗糙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.92,0:12:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,武风与流线所形成的丰姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.43,0:12:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刀身宁静的光辉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.79,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及众人灌注于这把剑中的\N意念力量之强大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.10,0:12:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿为此剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.87,0:12:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,及吾等诸位骑士们的勇气\N而放手一搏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.08,0:13:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战骑的诸位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.78,0:13:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出击迎战!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.18,0:13:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有机体检查完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.55,0:13:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G要塞随时都可以出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.42,0:13:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右边的三个人\N要乖乖的坐好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.63,0:13:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.36,0:13:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次的作战目的有二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.03,0:13:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一个目的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.73,0:13:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摧毁攻击地球联合政府大楼\N的外星异种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.40,0:13:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而第二个目的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.84,0:13:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准有任何一个例外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.17,0:13:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部都要平安归来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.78,0:13:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神GRAVION
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出动!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要以最高速度出发啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.41,0:14:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你... 不去避难吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是最棒的特等席不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.98,0:14:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是超重神失败的话\N躲到哪里都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.45,0:14:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此即使只是多一秒钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.19,0:14:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都要留在\N我最钟爱的研究对象身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.12,0:14:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的确...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在所能做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.93,0:14:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有为他们祈求胜利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.40,0:14:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此\N就让我在此看尽一切吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.04,0:14:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看他们是不是\N真的是人类的希望所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 到达指定地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.31,0:14:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G战骑的各位\N立刻进入作战行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.75,0:14:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.75,0:14:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最高加速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.49,0:14:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让超重神一直冲到\N超过敌人的预测速度范围!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爷、媚月小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\NOK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.50,0:15:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉露小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.37,0:15:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.21,0:15:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后用远远超过\N敌人预测的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.15,0:15:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷挥剑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.50,0:15:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.18,0:15:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斗牙少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.24,0:15:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G万断剑在刚刚的冲击下\N已经无法再撑下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请快出击毁掉它...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.68,0:15:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.78,0:15:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G万断剑锋利度提升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.76,0:16:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它打算干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工学终结!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.71,0:16:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重飞弹万弹齐发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连G万断剑都没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.66,0:16:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道超重神的装备\N就到此为止了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.33,0:16:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办才好啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.30,0:16:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桑德曼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白银之牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.06,0:17:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是现在的他们\N应该能负担的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.37,0:17:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重毒蛇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.58,0:18:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重神...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.08,0:18:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要、要输了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.12,0:18:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作起来琉菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.52,0:18:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?斗牙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.03,0:18:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还没有输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.56,0:18:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...一起加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.57,0:18:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.90,0:18:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不可思议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.27,0:18:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不会有要输的感觉了呢~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.97,0:18:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.08,0:18:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是挺行的嘛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好美...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白银之牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.10,0:19:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是超重剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.00,0:19:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重剑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.64,0:19:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那才是超重剑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.18,0:19:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.92,0:19:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是把能开拓出人类未来的牙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.69,0:19:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超重剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工学暴风!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.74,0:19:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超! 重! 断!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.83,0:20:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连攻击对象的空间\N都一起一刀两断了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.77,0:20:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,操控重力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.00,0:20:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还连空间都征服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.31,0:20:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也得尽早\N让我们的王牌完成才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.51,0:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了! 立花少尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经尽力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.69,0:20:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一回到城里\N就马上帮你修好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英司少爷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们也都表现的不错呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.63,0:20:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂! 告诉我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.94,0:20:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要战斗多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.24,0:20:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才能带我去见绫香啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪恶、悔恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.22,0:20:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及悲哀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.42,0:20:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人无论在哪个时代\N都不断在重复着相同的错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.09,0:21:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.29,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那群年轻人的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.32,0:21:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许可以跨越我们的愚昧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.83,0:21:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不敢寄望\N他们能够理解我们的罪过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.53,0:21:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.40,0:21:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当这一切都结束的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.24,0:21:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将到你的身边去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.72,0:21:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着在烈阳热气下\N道路的那一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.23,0:21:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形形色色的事物\N呈现形形色色的摆动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.27,0:21:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知该为何这般\N心头思绪纷乱不已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.01,0:22:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就这么视而不见\N朝向明日飞去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.52,0:22:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为无法接受如此的不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.86,0:22:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才说出了这么不客气的话语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.23,0:22:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若只是孤单一人地强出头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.14,0:22:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换来的只有误解\N矛盾与迷惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.94,0:22:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于那牵系着悲伤的羁绊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.18,0:22:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让微笑的双眸中渗出了泪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.68,0:22:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多想将这暖意传送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.49,0:22:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便紧握着手一直不愿放开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.32,0:22:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让这祈祷得以传达